#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:26
msgid "{sle-micro} clients require a reboot after registering."
msgstr "{sle-micro} clients requereixen un reinici després de registrar-se."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:27
msgid "Following the bootstrapping process, automatic booting is disabled on {sle-micro} clients. This change was implemented due to intermittent automatic reboots, which could occurr before {salt} could relay the results of applying the bootstrap {salt} state."
msgstr "Després del procés d'arrencada, l'arrencada automàtica està desactivada en {sle-micro} clients. Aquest canvi es va implementar a causa dels reinicis automàtics intermitents, que podrien produir-se abans que {salt} pogués transmetre els resultats de l'aplicació de l'estat d'arrencada {salt}."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:28
msgid "Although a reboot is automatically scheduled after registration is completed, it is respecting the default reboot manager maintenance window.  This window may be several hours after the client is registered.  It is advisable to manually reboot the client after the registration script finishes, to speed up the registration and to see the system appear in the system list."
msgstr "Tot i que un reinici es programa automàticament després de completar el registre, es respecta la finestra predeterminada de manteniment del gestor de reinici.  Aquesta finestra pot ser diverses hores després que el client estigui registrat.  És aconsellable reiniciar manualment el client un cop finalitzat el script de registre, per accelerar el registre i per veure el sistema apareix a la llista de sistemes."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:29
msgid "When using a bootstrap script with {sle-micro} systems, ensure that the certificate section of the script has this content:"
msgstr "Quan utilitzeu un script d'arrencada amb sistemes {sle-micro}, assegureu-vos que la secció de certificat de l'script tingui aquest contingut:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:30
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slmicro.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"ORG_CA_CERT=RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT\n"
"ORG_CA_CERT_IS_RPM_YN=0\n"
msgstr ""
"ORGCACERT=RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT\n"
"ORGCACERTISRPMYN00\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:31
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slmicro.adoc:28
msgid "Either edit the bootstrap script directly and add the settings, or create the bootstrap script with these parameters:"
msgstr "O bé editeu l'script bootstrap directament i afegiu la configuració, o creeu l'script bootstrap amb aquests paràmetres:"

#.  2023-12-12, ke: remains in /srv, see
#.  https://github.com/uyuni-project/uyuni-docs/pull/2682/files#r1423757456
#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:32
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"mgrctl exec -ti -- mgr-bootstrap --script=bootstrap-sle-micro.sh \\\n"
"    --ssl-cert=/srv/www/htdocs/pub/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT\n"
msgstr ""
"mgrctl exec -ti -- mgr-bootstrap --script-bootstrap-sle-micro.sh \\\n"
"    --ssl-cert//srv/www/htdocs/pub/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Reboot {sle-micro}"
msgstr "Reinicia {sle-micro}"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:34
msgid "{sle-micro} is a transactional system.  Transactional updates in general support several reboot methods.  It is recommended to use [systemitem]``systemd`` for rebooting in systems managed by {productname}.  Using other methods can lead to undesired behavior."
msgstr "{sle-micro} és un sistema transaccional.  Les actualitzacions transaccionals en general suporten diversos mètodes de reinici.  Es recomana utilitzar [systemitem] tosystemd to per reiniciar en sistemes gestionats per {productname}.  L'ús d'altres mètodes pot conduir a un comportament no desitjat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:35
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slmicro.adoc:32
msgid "When bootstrapping a transactional system on {productname}, [systemitem]``systemd`` will be configured as the reboot method ([literal]``REBOOT_METHOD``), if the system is in its default configuration.  Such a configuration allows {productname} to control the reboot action, and rebooting can be performed immediately or scheduled with {productname} as wanted."
msgstr "En arrencar un sistema transaccional a {productname}, [systemitem],systemd, es configurarà com a mètode de reinici ([literal].REBOOTMETHOD.), si el sistema està en la seva configuració predeterminada.  Aquesta configuració permet que {productname} controli l'acció de reinici, i es pot reiniciar immediatament o programar amb {productname} com es vulgui."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:37
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slmicro.adoc:34
msgid "By default, the reboot method during client installation is set to [option]``auto``.  With the [option]``auto`` boot method, [command]``rebootmgrd`` will be used to reboot the system according to the configured policies if the service is running.  Policies can be to reboot instantly or during a maintenance window.  For more information, see the [command]``rebootmgrd``(8) man page.  Otherwise if [command]``rebootmgrd`` is not running, {productname} will call [command]``systemctl reboot``."
msgstr "Per defecte, el mètode de reinici durant la instal·lació del client està establert a [option].auto..  Amb el mètode d'arrencada [option].auto,, [command].rebootmgrd. s'utilitzarà per reiniciar el sistema d'acord amb les polítiques configurades si el servei s'està executant.  Les polítiques poden ser reiniciar instantàniament o durant una finestra de manteniment.  Per a més informació, vegeu la pàgina del manual [ordre].rebootmgrd.(8).  En cas contrari, si [ordred].rebootmgrd, no s'està executant, {productname} cridarà [ordred].systemctl reboot.."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slemicro.adoc:38
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-slmicro.adoc:35
msgid "Using any method different from [command]``systemd`` may cause undesired behavior."
msgstr "L'ús de qualsevol mètode diferent de [ordre].sistema may pot causar un comportament no desitjat."

#.  2023-05-23, ke: The rest is commented and the user will not see the
#.                  following remarks/background info:
#. Otherwise, the only thing mlm will be able to do is to ask for a reboot and it will be managed in the peculiarities of each reboot method. Not having control of when the reboot should happen, also takes away from mlm the ability to perform the reboot on its own maintenance windows, which is not the ideal configuration.
#. The user must be able to change reboot method at any time and SUSE Manager will keep it. But in this case we should alert in the documentation that using any method different from systemd may cause undesired behavior.
#. type: Title =
