#, no-wrap
msgid "Registering {sll} Clients"
msgstr "S'estan registrant {sle} clients"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-sleses.adoc:2
msgid "This section contains information about registering clients running {sll} operating systems.  {sll} clients are based on {rhel} or {centos}."
msgstr "Aquesta secció conté informació sobre el registre de clients que executen sistemes operatius {sll}.  {sll} clients es basen en {rhel} o {centos}."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-sleses.adoc:3
msgid "{sll} clients are sometimes also called {sleses} (SLESES), Liberty, RES or {redhat} {es}."
msgstr "Els clients {sll} de vegades també s'anomenen {sleses} (SLESES), Liberty, RES o {redhat} {es}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-sleses.adoc:4
msgid "The {sll} software channels provided by {suse} only provide updates to packages, they do not provide the packages themselves.  To register {sll} clients, you need to register the {sll} Product (outlined below) to create the necessary base channel, then import any required {redhat} or {centos} packages as custom child channels.  You must obtain the initial packages directly from {redhat} or {centos} before you can apply the updates provided by the {sll} software channels."
msgstr "Els canals de programari {sll} proporcionats per {suse} només proporcionen actualitzacions als paquets, no proporcionen els mateixos paquets.  Per registrar {sll} clients, heu de registrar el producte {sll} (esborrat a continuació) per crear el canal base necessari, i després importar qualsevol paquet {redhat} o {centos} requerit com a canals fills personalitzats.  Heu d'obtenir els paquets inicials directament de {redhat} o {centos} abans de poder aplicar les actualitzacions proporcionades pels canals de programari {sll}."

