#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-sleses.adoc:9
msgid "You must obtain support from {suse} for all your {sll} systems."
msgstr "Heu d'obtenir suport de {suse} per a tots els vostres sistemes {sll}."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-sleses.adoc:10
