#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-sleses.adoc:13
msgid "The {sll} product is provided by {scclongform}.  This also includes the client tools package."
msgstr "El producte {sll} és proporcionat per {scclongform}.  Això també inclou el paquet d'eines del client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/clients-sleses.adoc:14
