#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:44
msgid "The SSH Push feature uses taskomatic to execute scheduled actions using [command]``salt-ssh``.  The taskomatic job periodically checks for scheduled actions and executes them.  The SSH Push feature executes a complete [command]``salt-ssh`` call based on the scheduled action."
msgstr "La característica SSH Push utilitza taskomatic per a executar accions programades utilitzant [ordre].salt-ssh..  El treball taskomatic comprova periòdicament les accions programades i les executa.  La funció SSH Push executa una crida completa [ordre].salt-ssh. basada en l'acció programada."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:45
msgid "By default, twenty Salt SSH actions can be executed at a time.  You can increase the number of actions that can be executed in parallel, by adding these lines to your configuration file, and adjusting the value of ``parallel_threads`` upwards.  We recommend you keep the number of parallel actions low, to avoid problems:"
msgstr "Per defecte, es poden executar vint accions Salt SSH alhora.  Podeu augmentar el nombre d'accions que es poden executar en paral·lel, afegint aquestes línies al fitxer de configuració i ajustant el valor de .parallelthreads. cap amunt.  Us recomanem mantenir baix el nombre d'accions paral·leles, per evitar problemes:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:46
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"taskomatic.sshminion_action_executor.parallel_threads = <number>\n"
"org.quartz.threadPool.threadCount = <value of parallel_threads + 20>\n"
msgstr ""
"taskomatic.sshminion_action_executor.parallel_threads = <number>\n"
"org.quartz.threadPool.threadCount = <value of parallel_threads + 20>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:47
msgid "This adjusts the number of actions that can run in parallel on any one client and the total number of worker threads used by taskomatic.  If actions needs to be run on multiple clients, actions are always executed sequentially on each client."
msgstr "Això ajusta el nombre d'accions que poden executar-se en paral·lel en qualsevol client i el nombre total de fils de treball utilitzats per taskomatic.  Si les accions s'han d'executar en múltiples clients, les accions sempre s'executen seqüencialment en cada client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/contact-methods-saltssh.adoc:48
msgid "If the clients are connected through a proxy, you need to adjust the ``MaxSessions`` settings on the proxy.  In this case, set the number of parallel connections to be three times the total number of clients."
msgstr "Si els clients estan connectats a través d'un servidor intermediari, heu d'ajustar la configuració de .MaxSessions. al servidor intermediari.  En aquest cas, establir el nombre de connexions paral·leles a tres vegades el nombre total de clients."

