msgstr "A {productname} {webui}, navegueu al menú:Systems[Llista de sistemes] i seleccioneu el client a suprimir."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:8
msgid "Click btn:[Delete System]."
msgstr "Feu clic a btn:[Suprimeix el sistema]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:9
msgid "Check the details and click btn:[Delete Profile] to confirm."
msgstr "Comproveu els detalls i feu clic a btn:[Suprimeix el perfil] per a confirmar-ho."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:10
msgid "For Salt clients, {productname} attempts to clean up additional configuration.  If the client cannot be contacted, you are given the option to cancel the deletion, or delete the client without cleaning up the configuration files."
msgstr "Per als clients de Salt, {productname} intenta netejar la configuració addicional.  Si no es pot contactar amb el client, se li dona l'opció de cancel·lar la supressió, o eliminar el client sense netejar els fitxers de configuració."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:11
msgid "You can also delete multiple clients using the System Set Manager.  For more information about the System Set Manager, see xref:client-configuration:system-set-manager.adoc[]."
msgstr "Podeu aplicar accions de gestió d'energia a múltiples clients al mateix temps, afegint-les al gestor de conjunts de sistemes.  Per obtenir més informació sobre l'ús del gestor de conjunts de sistemes, vegeu xref:client-configuration:system-set-manager.adoc[]."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:12
msgid "Cleaning up a client only disables {salt} and stops the service if possible.  It does not uninstall the package."
msgstr "La neteja d'un client només desactiva {salt} i atura el servei si és possible.  No desinstal·la el paquet."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Delete a Client on the Command Line (with API Call)"
msgstr "Suprimeix un client a la línia d'ordres (amb crida API)"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Deleting a Client from the Server"
msgstr "Procediment: Suprimir un client"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:15
msgid "Delete the client with the FQDN (Fully Qualified Domain Name):"
msgstr "Suprimeix el client amb el FQDN (Nom de domini complet):"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "spacecmd system_delete FQDN\n"
msgstr "spacecmd systemdelete FQDN\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:17
msgid "[command]``spacecmd system_delete`` also deletes the {salt} key."
msgstr "[command].spacecmd systemdelete. també elimina la tecla {salt}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:18
msgid "[command]``system_delete`` offers the following options:"
msgstr "[ordre]:systemdelete the ofereix les següents opcions:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "usage: system_delete [options] <SYSTEMS>\n"
msgstr "ús: systemdelete [opcions] <SYSTEMS>\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/delete-clients.adoc:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    options:\n"
"          -c TYPE - Possible values:\n"
"             *  'FAIL_ON_CLEANUP_ERR' - fail in case of cleanup error,\n"
"             *  'NO_CLEANUP' - do not cleanup, just delete,\n"
"             *  'FORCE_DELETE' - try cleanup first but delete server anyway\n"
"\t        in case of error\n"
msgstr ""
"    opcions:\n"
"          -c TIPUS - Valors possibles:\n"
"             * 'FAILONCLEANUPERR' - falla en cas d'error de neteja,\n"
"             * 'NOCLEANUP' - no netejar, només esborrar,\n"
"             * 'FORCEDELETE' - intenteu netejar primer però suprimiu el servidor de totes maneres\n"
"\t        en cas d'error\n"

