#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:2
msgid "Operating systems either trust their own GPG keys directly or at least ship them installed with the minimal system.  But third party packages signed by a different GPG key need manual handling.  The clients can be successfully bootstrapped without the GPG key being trusted.  However, you cannot install new client tool packages or update them until the keys are trusted."
msgstr "Els sistemes operatius o bé confien directament en les seves pròpies claus GPG o almenys les envien instal·lades amb el sistema mínim.  Però els paquets de tercers signats per una clau GPG diferent necessiten una gestió manual.  Els clients poden arrencar amb èxit sense que es confiï en la clau GPG.  No obstant això, no podeu instal·lar nous paquets d'eines de client o actualitzar-los fins que es confiï en les claus."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:3
msgid "Clients now use GPG key information entered for a software channel to manage the trusted keys.  When a software channel with GPG key information is assigned to a client, the key is trusted when the channel is refreshed or the first package is installed from this channel."
msgstr "Els clients ara utilitzen la informació de la clau GPG introduïda per a un canal de programari per gestionar les claus de confiança.  Quan un canal de programari amb informació de clau GPG s'assigna a un client, la clau és de confiança quan el canal s'actualitza o el primer paquet s'instal·la des d'aquest canal."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:4
msgid "The GPG key URL parameter in the software channel page can contain multiple key URLs separated by \"whitespace\".  In case it is a file URL, the GPG key file must be deployed on the client before the software channel is used."
msgstr "El paràmetre d'URL de la clau GPG a la pàgina del canal de programari pot contenir múltiples URL de claus separades per \"espais en blanc\".  En el cas que es tracti d'un URL de fitxer, el fitxer de clau GPG s'ha de desplegar al client abans d'utilitzar el canal de programari."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:5
msgid "The GPG keys for the Client Tools Channels of {redhat} based clients are deployed on the client into [path]``/etc/pki/rpm-gpg/`` and can be referenced with file URLs."
msgstr "Les claus GPG per als canals d'eines de client de {redhat} basats en clients es despleguen al client a [path]./etc/pki/rpm-gpg/. i es poden fer referències amb URL de fitxer."

#.  SUSE Liberty Linux not available at Uyuni for now
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:6
msgid "Same is the case with the GPG keys of {sll} clients."
msgstr "El mateix passa amb les claus GPG dels clients {sll}."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:7
msgid "Only in case a software channel is assigned to the client they will be imported and trusted by the system."
msgstr "Només en el cas que s'assigni un canal de programari al client serà importat i de confiança pel sistema."

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:8
msgid "Because Debian based systems sign only metadata, there is no need to specify extra keys for single channels.  If a user configures an own GPG key to sign the metadata as described in \"Use Your Own GPG Key\" in xref:administration:repo-metadata.adoc[] the deployment and trust of that key is executed automatically."
msgstr "Com que els sistemes basats en Debian només signen metadades, no hi ha necessitat d'especificar claus addicionals per a canals individuals.  Si un usuari configura una clau GPG pròpia per signar les metadades tal com es descriu a \"Utilitza la teva pròpia clau GPG\" a xref:administration:repo-metadata.adoc[] el desplegament i la confiança d'aquesta clau s'executa automàticament."

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "User Defined GPG Keys"
msgstr "Usa la vostra pròpia clau GPG"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:10
msgid "Users can define custom GPG keys to be deployed to a client."
msgstr "Els usuaris poden definir claus GPG personalitzades que s'han de desplegar a un client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:11
msgid "By providing some pillar data and providing the GPG key files in the {salt} filesystem, they are automatically deployed to the client."
msgstr "En proporcionar algunes dades de pilar i proporcionar els fitxers de clau GPG en el sistema de fitxers {salt}, es despleguen automàticament al client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:12
msgid "These keys are deployed into [path]``/etc/pki/rpm-gpg/`` on RPM based operating systems and to [path]``/usr/share/keyrings/`` on Debian systems:"
msgstr "Aquestes claus es despleguen a [path]:/etc/pki/rpm-gpg/: en sistemes operatius basats en RPM i a [path] and/usr/share/keyrings/: en sistemes Debian:"

#.  I think the cat command is here to show the contents of the file.
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:13
msgid "Define the pillar key [literal``custom_gpgkeys`` for the client you want to deploy the key to and list the names of the key file."
msgstr "Definiu la clau de pilar [literal.customgpgkeys. per al client que voleu desplegar la clau i llistar els noms del fitxer de clau."

#.  In this case, the cat is superfluous.
#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"cat /srv/pillar/mypillar.sls\n"
"custom_gpgkeys:\n"
"  - my_first_gpg.key\n"
"  - my_second_gpgkey.gpg\n"
msgstr ""
"gat /srv/pillar/mypillar.sls\n"
"tecles personalitzades:\n"
"  - myfirstgpg.key\n"
"  - mysecondgpgkey.gpg\n"

#.  I think the ls command is here to show the contents of the directory.
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:15
msgid "Additionally in the {salt} filesystem create a directory named [path]``gpg`` and store there the GPG key files with the name specified in the [iteral]``custom_gpgkeys`` pillar data."
msgstr "A més, en el sistema de fitxers {salt} creeu un directori anomenat [camí].gpg. i deseu allà els fitxers de claus GPG amb el nom especificat en les dades del pilar [iteral].customgpgkeys.."

#.  In this case, the ls is superfluous.
#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:16
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"ls -la /srv/salt/gpg/\n"
"/srv/salt/gpg/my_first_gpg.key\n"
"/srv/salt/gpg/my_second_gpgkey.gpg\n"
msgstr ""
"ls -la /srv/salt/gpg/\n"
"/srv/salt/gpg/myfirstgpg.key\n"
"/srv/salt/gpg/mysecondgpgkey.gpg\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:17
msgid "The keys are deployed to the client at [path]``/etc/pki/rpm-gpg/my_first_gpg.key`` and [path]``/etc/pki/rpm-gpg/my_second_gpgkey.gpg``."
msgstr "Les claus es despleguen al client a [path]./etc/pki/rpm-gpg/myfirstgpg.key. i [path]./etc/pki/rpm-gpg/mysecondgpgkey.gpg.."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/snippets/trust_gpg.adoc:18
msgid "The last step is to add the URL to the GPG key URL field of the software channel.  Navigate to menu:Software[Manage > Channels] and select the channel you want to modify.  Add to [guimenu]``GPG key URL`` the value [literal]``file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/my_first_gpg.key``."
msgstr "L'últim pas és afegir l'URL al camp de la clau GPG del canal de programari.  Navega al menú:Software[Gestiona . Canals] i selecciona el canal que vols modificar.  Afegeix a [guimenu].URL de la clau GPG. el valor [literal].file:///etc/pki/rpm-gpg/myfirstgpg.key.."

