#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-set-manager.adoc:3
msgid "The system set manager (SSM) is used to perform actions on more than one client at a time.  SSM creates ephemeral sets of clients, making it useful for one-off actions that you need to apply to a number of clients.  If you want more permanent sets, consider using system groups instead.  For more information about system groups, see xref:client-configuration:system-groups.adoc[]."
