msgid "Navigate to menu:Systems[System Groups], and click btn:[Use in SSM] for the system group you want to work with."
msgstr "Navega al menú:Sistemes[Grups de sistema], i fes clic a btn:[Usa a SSM] per al grup de sistema amb el qual vulguis treballar."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-set-manager.adoc:13
msgid "Navigate to menu:Systems[System Groups], check the group you want to work with, and click btn:[Work with Group]."
