#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-set-manager.adoc:15
msgid "The details in SSM might differ slightly from the details in other parts of the {productname} {webui}.  In SSM, all available updates are shown.  This allows you to upgrade to packages that might not be the latest version."
