#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-set-manager.adoc:24
msgid "Select the new base channel in the [guimenu]``Desired base Channel`` field, and click btn:[Next]."
msgstr "Seleccioneu el canal base nou al camp [guimenu]].Canal base desitjat]. i feu clic a btn:[Següent]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/system-set-manager.adoc:25
