msgid "{suse} is a Nutanix ecosystem partner and {productname} has obtained the Nutanix-ready certification in the \"Nutanix AHV integrated\" category."
msgstr "{suse} és soci de l'ecosistema de Nutanix i SUSE Manager ha obtingut la certificació Nutanix-ready en la categoria \"Nutanix AHV integrated\"."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-nutanix.adoc:3
msgid "For more information about Nutanix integrations, see https://www.nutanix.com/partners/technology-alliances/suse"
