#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/vhm-nutanix.adoc:4
msgid "You can use Nutanix AHV virtual machines with {productname} by setting up a virtual host manager (VHM).  To begin, you need to set up a VHM on your {productname} Server, and inventory the available VM hosts."
